            "image_mb": "shopify://shop_images/GT50_dirt_bike_60V30ah_m.jpg",
            "image_pos": "right",
            "title": "<p><strong>60V 30Ah </strong>Long-Lasting Battery</p>",
            "content": "<p>The 60V 30Ah battery delivers up to 80 miles of max range, making the GT50 ready for long commutes, weekend adventures, and extended outdoor rides. With BMS battery management, fast 6–8 hour charging, and overheating protection, the system is built for safer and more efficient energy use.</p>",
