        "item_6M3dHz": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_margin_top": 96,
            "item_margin_bottom": 60,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/GT50_dirt_bike_hydraulic_fork.jpg",
            "image_mb": "shopify://shop_images/GT50_dirt_bike_hydraulic_fork_m.jpg",
            "image_pos": "left",
            "title": "<p>Reduce Bumps by <strong>Up to 90%</strong></p>",
            "content": "<p>The GT50 uses hydraulic front forks, nitrogen rear damping, and an extended 23-inch sponge saddle to absorb road impact and reduce vibration. From potholes and gravel to dirt trails and uneven rural roads, the full shock absorption system helps deliver a smoother, more stable ride.</p>",
            "param_title_1": "",
            "param_content_1": "",
            "param_title_2": "",
            "param_content_2": ""
          }
        },
        "item_VNaYcH": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_margin_top": 60,
            "item_margin_bottom": 60,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/GT50_dirt_bike_tire.jpg",
            "image_mb": "shopify://shop_images/GT50_dirt_bike_tire_m.jpg",
            "image_pos": "right",
            "title": "<p>Ready for Multiple Road Conditions</p>",
            "content": "<p>The GT50 rides on wide 20\" x 3.0\" motorcycle-style tires with aggressive tread for dependable traction. Provides confident traction and stability across beach roads, snow roads, mountain roads, rural roads, gravel, mud, and daily pavement. Whether you are exploring outdoors or commuting through mixed terrain, the GT50 is built to keep you moving.</p>",
            "param_title_1": "",
            "param_content_1": "",
            "param_title_2": "",
            "param_content_2": ""
          }
        },
        "item_zmQHGy": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_margin_top": 60,
            "item_margin_bottom": 60,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/GT50_dirt_bike_braking.jpg",
            "image_mb": "shopify://shop_images/GT50_dirt_bike_braking_m.jpg",
            "image_pos": "left",
            "title": "<p>Instant, Reliable Braking</p>",
            "content": "<p>The GT50 features dual hydraulic disc brakes that deliver quick, responsive, and reliable stopping power. Compared with ordinary brakes, the hydraulic braking system improves braking safety and precision, helping you stay in control during high-speed riding, downhill sections, turns, and emergency stops.</p>",
            "param_title_1": "",
            "param_content_1": "",
            "param_title_2": "",
